response.original_title: America's Most Wanted: John Walsh's Dirty Dozen
response.overview: As prolific and Emmy-Award winning series host John Walsh hits a milestone of hosting 1,100 episodes of America's Most Wanted and helping capture 1,198 fugitives, America's Most Wanted: John Walsh's Dirty Dozen looks back at the origin story of this groundbreaking true crime series and how America's Most Wanted began back in 1988
response.title: America's Most Wanted: John Walsh's Dirty Dozen
